{
  "argument_loc": "Local",
  "description": "Order the given unit(s) to follow another from his own group as his [[formLeader|formation leader]] (without radio messages).<br>\nIt is also used to order the unit to '''return to formation''' after e.g [[doStop]] even if it is the leader himself that should return to formation (see [[#Example 2|Example 2]]).",
